# Azure Application Gateway ARM Template

This directory contains ARM templates and deployment scripts for Azure Application Gateway.

## Quick Links

- **[Complete Documentation](README.md)** - Comprehensive guide with all features and configuration options
- **[Deployment Guide](DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE.md)** - Step-by-step deployment instructions
- **[Main Template](ApplicationGateway.json)** - ARM template file
- **[Parameters](parameters.json)** - Sample parameters file
- **[PowerShell Script](deploy.ps1)** - Automated deployment script for Windows
- **[Bash Script](deploy.sh)** - Automated deployment script for Linux/macOS

## Quick Start

1. Edit `parameters.json` with your values
2. Run `.\deploy.ps1 -ResourceGroupName "your-rg" -Location "eastus"`
3. Follow post-deployment configuration steps

For detailed instructions, see [DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE.md](DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE.md)